              "sentence": "On 8 July, Jordan Bardella, president of the French National Rally (RN), was named as the group's president",
              "refs": []
            },
            {
              "sentence": "The Polish Confederation's National Movement, which won two MEPs, announced in July 2024 that it was in negotiations with Patriots for Europe, while the three Confederation MEPs from New Hope joined the ESN group, and the one Confederation of the Polish Crown MEP was not seeking to join",
